In [125]:
#Preparacion de datos para el modelo
X = datos.drop(variable_objetivo, axis = 1)
y = datos[variable_objetivo]

pre = [('initial',ColumnTransformer([("selector", 'passthrough',selected_cols)])),
       ('imputer', SimpleImputer(missing_values=np.nan, strategy='median')),
       ('scaler', MinMaxScaler())]

modelo = [('model', LinearRegression())]

pipe = Pipeline(pre+modelo)

pipe = pipe.fit(X,y)
In [126]:
# Exportacion a Joblib:
filename = '/content/drive/MyDrive/Colab Notebooks/LabBI/Lab-4/modelo.joblib'
dump(pipe, filename)
